  "title": "Senior Instrumentation & Control Engineer (PLC) Oil & Gas",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is from Oil and Gas industry, a local leading player. They are looking for a Senior Engineer, Instrumentation &amp; Control for the next phase of their business. They are located in West.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide technical support for Production and Maintenance teams on instrument-related issues.</li>\n  <li>Work with teams to reduce instrument maintenance costs and improve functionality.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with external stakeholders on gas pipeline networks, electrical grids, instruments, and metering interfaces.</li>\n  <li>Update maintenance procedures for instruments, PLC, Fire &amp; Gas systems, ESD, metering, CCTV, and security equipment.</li>\n  <li>Conduct root cause analysis for instrument incidents and recommend preventive actions.</li>\n  <li>Implement MOC projects to enhance instrument reliability and operational efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Ensure verification, inspection, testing, and certification of electrical and instrument equipment in hazardous areas.</li>\n  <li>Support maintenance and major equipment turnarounds.</li>\n  <li>Manage the functional safety lifecycle of SIS in the terminal.</li>\n  <li>Assist in expansion projects, ensuring facility integrity and seamless integration.</li>\n  <li>Participate in emergency response with designated roles and responsibilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Bachelor’s Degree in Engineering related field.</li>\n  <li>Min 5 years’ experience in Oil &amp; Gas or Petrochemical industry</li>\n  <li>Experience in instrument &amp; control maintenance</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9682</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
